| [tailwind-merge](https://github.com/dcastil/tailwind-merge) | 3.x | MIT | Tailwind Class Merge |
| [react-markdown](https://github.com/remarkjs/react-markdown) | 10.x | MIT | Markdown Renderer |
| [remark-gfm](https://github.com/remarkjs/remark-gfm) | 5.x | MIT | GitHub Flavored Markdown |

